@startuml
title Spring Boot4 MCP Demo - 系统架构图

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "用户" as User

package "MCP Client (port 8081)" as Client {
  component "Controllers" as Ctrl

  rectangle "服务层" {
    component ChatClient as ChatClient
    component RAGService as RAGSvc
    component SearXNGService as SearXNSvc
    component SSEServerComponent as SSE
  }
}

package "MCP 服务器" as MCP {
  component "mcp-server1\nSSE :8082" as S1
  component "mcp-server2\nStdio" as S2
  component "百度地图 MCP" as Baidu
}

database "Redis Stack\n向量存储\n记忆存储\n:8379" as Redis
database "SearXNG\n搜索引擎\n:8381" as SearXNG

User --> Ctrl : HTTP 请求

ChatClient --> MCP : MCP 工具调用
ChatClient <--> Redis : 读写对话记忆

ChatClient --> MCP : MCP 工具调用(无记忆)

RAGSvc --> Redis : 向量存储
RAGSvc --> ChatClient : LLM 增强回答

SearXNSvc --> SearXNG : HTTP 搜索
SearXNSvc --> ChatClient : AI 总结搜索结果

note right of Ctrl
  ChatController → ChatClient / ChatClient : 聊天
  RAGController → RAGSvc : 知识库
  SearXNGController → SearXNSvc : 搜索
  SSEController → SSE : 推送
end note

note right of ChatClient
  会话 ID 隔离多租户多用户数据
end note

@enduml
